Liza Figueroa Kravinsky https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liza_Figueroa_Kravinsky 0 Liza Figueroa Kravinsky (born 1962) is an American composer, filmmaker, and actress living in Arlington, Virginia, USA. She is best known for composing the Go-Go Symphony and founding the Go-Go Symphony ensemble. She is also the filmmaker of the documentary Beauty in the Eyes of the Beheld.
